{"HICCOUGH":[{"def":"To have a hiccough or hiccoughs.","pos":""}],"HICKORY":[{"def":"An American tree of the genus Carya, of which there are several species.","pos":""}],"HICKSITE":[{"def":"A member or follower of the \"liberal\" party, headed by Elias Hicks, which, because of a change of views respecting the divinity of Christ and the Atonement, seceded from the conservative portion of the Society of Friends in the United States, in 1827.","pos":""}],"HICKUP":[{"def":"The lesser spotted woodpecker (Dendrocopus minor) of Europe.","pos":""}]}